<title>USA: Loehmann's Q1 same-store sales off 6.2 pct.</title>
<headline>Loehmann's Q1 same-store sales off 6.2 pct.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-05-08</dateline>
<text>
<p>Percent change</p>
<p>		    1997	     1996	  Total   Same-Store</p>
<p>Q1		  $112.6     $104.1    +n/a	-6.2</p>
<p>NOTE: Figures in millions except percentage.</p>
<p>Full company name is Loehmann's Inc</p>
<p>Note: The company said in early April it expected earnings for the first quarter ended May 3 to fall well below expectations, to between $0.14 and $0.20 compared to earnings of $0.32 a share last year.</p>
<p>It cited lower same-store sales and high costs to open three new stores ahead of schedule for the Q1 shortfall.</p>
<p>-- New York Newsdesk 212-859-1610</p>
